# ccBitTorrent Project Structure

## Core Architecture
This is a high-performance BitTorrent client with modern architecture:

- **Main Entry**: [ccbt/__main__.py](mdc:ccbt/__main__.py) - CLI entry point
- **Session Management**: [ccbt/session.py](mdc:ccbt/session.py) - Main client session
- **Configuration**: [ccbt/config.py](mdc:ccbt/config.py) - Configuration management with Pydantic models
- **Models**: [ccbt/models.py](mdc:ccbt/models.py) - Pydantic data models and validation

## Key Components

### Core BitTorrent Implementation
- [ccbt/torrent.py](mdc:ccbt/torrent.py) - Torrent file handling and metadata
- [ccbt/peer.py](mdc:ccbt/peer.py) - Peer connection management
- [ccbt/peer_connection.py](mdc:ccbt/peer_connection.py) - Peer connection logic
- [ccbt/async_peer_connection.py](mdc:ccbt/async_peer_connection.py) - Async peer connections
- [ccbt/piece_manager.py](mdc:ccbt/piece_manager.py) - Piece selection and management
- [ccbt/tracker.py](mdc:ccbt/tracker.py) - Tracker communication
- [ccbt/dht.py](mdc:ccbt/dht.py) - Distributed Hash Table implementation

### Advanced Features
- [ccbt/security/](mdc:ccbt/security/) - Security enhancements and ML features
- [ccbt/ml/](mdc:ccbt/ml/) - Machine learning optimizations
- [ccbt/monitoring/](mdc:ccbt/monitoring/) - Advanced monitoring and observability
- [ccbt/observability/](mdc:ccbt/observability/) - Performance profiling and debugging

### CLI and Interface
- [ccbt/cli/](mdc:ccbt/cli/) - Enhanced CLI with Rich interface
- [ccbt/events.py](mdc:ccbt/events.py) - Event-driven architecture
- [ccbt/exceptions.py](mdc:ccbt/exceptions.py) - Exception hierarchy

## Development Patterns
- **Async/Await**: All I/O operations are asynchronous
- **Event-Driven**: Components communicate via events
- **Service-Oriented**: Modular service architecture
- **Plugin System**: Extensible plugin architecture
- **Type Safety**: Comprehensive type hints with Pydantic validation